    "description": "Pirate Dragons is a third-person, action RPG where you play a dragon in a world filled with sailing ships, islands, trade routes, pirates, and much more. <br><br>Battle against other sailing ships from different factions, grow your dragon's power, learn new breath weapons, build your own sailing fleet, and make your mark!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835120/extras/5c0428fedd7a10aee16f35e74e59227b.poster.avif?t=1755324089\" width=600 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835120/extras/5c0428fedd7a10aee16f35e74e59227b.webm?t=1755324089\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835120/extras/5c0428fedd7a10aee16f35e74e59227b.mp4?t=1755324089\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play a dragon!<br></li><li>Third-person, high flying, action combat.<br></li><li>Explore an open world of islands, sailing ships, and piracy.<br></li><li>Use power-ups to increase your fire damage, heal you, and recharge your breath weapons.<br></li><li>Level up to learn new breath weapons and other skills.<br></li><li>Build a fleet of ships to help you trade goods and battle against other factions.<br></li><li>Upgrade your ships with better crews, sails, cannons, and hulls.<br></li><li>Complete missions, become a merchant, or engage in piracy!<br></li><li>An economy that changes based on your actions.<br></li><li>Events and missions.<br></li><li>Grow your hoard to become the richest and most powerful dragon ever!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1835120/extras/13ae70d0beb70ca16af20918a95478c8.poster.avif?t=1755324089\